{
  "stem": "26792.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I didn't have to live in any camps, like the others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I lived a-- we lived in a [NON-ENGLISH] in [NON-ENGLISH], it's called, in Stockholm-- a suburb.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A beautiful suburb.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A day or two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No more.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the first place, I found as many Jewish people as I could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got to [? a ?] [NON-ENGLISH], and-- well, and there were, you know, I was young then, and-- and I was having a good time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vaboulis was staying at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was depressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was going with my-- out with my Jewish friends, making trips and going to different parties and working hard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Working hard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at home, we invited people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only his friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His friends.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later, very, very many boats arrived, one after the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw in the streets Latvians wearing German uniforms, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they arrived in-- Jew killers-- they arrived in the German uniforms, of the SS [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after I had heard from one of our guests that they had a drowned a Jew whom they had picked up in Windau in order to take him to Sweden, and then they had second thoughts, and they decided to show him the Swedish the Swedish land in the distance and, look, Jew.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is-- that is Sweden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That is freedom.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they threw him into the sea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have forgotten his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I rushed to the Swedish police, and I informed about that fact.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I mentioned the name of the people who told me, the man, exactly, who told me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I started looking for-- I was traveling from camp to camp, looking for these people, searching for them.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
